### 2. Layouts вЂ” Convert admin page to a proper Nuxt layout

#### [NEW] [admin.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/layouts/admin.vue)
- Move the entire sidebar + top bar + `<NuxtPage />` structure from [pages/admin.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin.vue) into a proper Nuxt layout file
- Replace `<NuxtPage />` with `<slot />` (Nuxt layout convention)

#### [MODIFY] [admin.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin.vue)
- Convert to a simple page that sets `definePageMeta({ layout: 'admin' })` and renders `<NuxtPage />`
- This keeps the nested route structure working

#### [MODIFY] Admin sub-pages ([queuing.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin/queuing.vue), [documents.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin/documents.vue), [assets.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin/assets.vue), [hr.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin/hr.vue), [waste.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin/waste.vue), [index.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/index.vue))
- No layout changes neededвЂ”they are nested under `pages/admin/` and inherit from the parent [pages/admin.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/admin.vue)

---

### 3. Layouts вЂ” Add a default layout

#### [NEW] [default.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/layouts/default.vue)
- Create a minimal default layout with `<slot />`
- Remove `definePageMeta({ layout: false })` from [index.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/index.vue) and [kiosk.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/kiosk.vue) since the default layout will be transparent

---

### 4. Components вЂ” Extract kiosk ticket modal

#### [NEW] [KioskTicketModal.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/components/kiosk/KioskTicketModal.vue)
- Extract the ticket printing modal (~60 lines of template + logic) from [kiosk.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/kiosk.vue) into a reusable component
- Props: `show`, `isPrinting`, `ticket` (the printed ticket data)
- Emits: [close](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/kiosk.vue#79-84)

#### [MODIFY] [kiosk.vue](file:///c:/Users/barra/OneDrive/Desktop/code/app-hms/app/pages/kiosk.vue)
- Replace inline modal with `<KioskTicketModal />`

